{"tid":1323822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721集會最新消息","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T02:29:22.000Z","uid":258416,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2885f5eceedd06ae75739d8a3ff8e8bfd0696a19","tid":1323822,"uid":258416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:19:58.000Z","msg":"民間人權陣線公告：<br />\n<br />\n民陣原定於7月21日的集會，警方稱基於公共安全考慮，建議將集會改期至8月。民陣表明拒絕，提出反建議在20或21日改為由銅鑼灣遊行到金鐘或中環。召集人岑子杰見記者強調，將集會改為遊行，已是提供彈性予警方考慮。民陣在會上表明將就遊行人士安全作出額外保障，以確保參與人士人身安全，惟詳情有待警方商討落實。<br />\n<br />\n就今個20或21日的行動詳情，民陣已促警方明天必須盡早進行會議，而我們將盡快向大家公佈。"},{"pid":"ad1979d50d73028c2481eef693eb574845953b45","tid":1323822,"uid":258416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:34:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b5e8ba63de00100a626a253bf865a5f64698e7c2","tid":1323822,"uid":272842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:01:37.000Z","msg":"721 push"},{"pid":"761ac8a3100076df52266f551130bccb6931f1ed","tid":1323822,"uid":8891,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:02:15.000Z","msg":"調轉金鐘去銅鑼灣啦"},{"pid":"2b2986b3ed919bb7d4054a1ffdccd377021cd905","tid":1323822,"uid":261802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:04:31.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"6985382bb5bf21a68c859d8b79977049bb0d2881","tid":1323822,"uid":22634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6b79c7be6543ce9a3a274bf9e97c3ecb9f1f06ac","tid":1323822,"uid":279159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b104cd7c69dd5e45a97c5dd5fdff0e7e585f7f73","tid":1323822,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:30:40.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"365a7d191af080474bf51a3bb9edafccfaad425f","tid":1323822,"uid":261095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:33:09.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br /